# $PACKAGE_NAME

Intro

## Project structure

```
Sources/$PACKAGE_NAME/              # Library source code
Tests/${PACKAGE_NAME}Tests/         # Unit tests
Example/${PACKAGE_NAME}App/         # Demo app (Xcode project via project.yml)
```

## Stack

- Swift 6, strict concurrency (`actor`, `Sendable`)
- SPM (swift-tools-version: 6.2)
- Minimum deployment: iOS 17
- Testing framework: Swift Testing (`import Testing`)
- Approachable concurrency: YES
- Default actor isolation: MainActor
- Strict concurrency checking: Complete
- SwiftLint via SPM build tool plugin

## Architecture

